Thank you very much for the bugreport and willing make free software better.
Could you please provide steps to reproduce that problem?

I am not certain, was just using the software. I think I had a very short network outage blink on a Comcast ISP. But that seemed to trigger the closing of the Remmina software. I can try making a connection and then dropping my network connection for a very short period and see what happens. Will report back if that is the trigger. Thanks, Devon
